zes="(max-width: 285px) 100vw, 285px" /></li></ul></div></div></p><p></em></p><p>&nbsp;</p> <a class="wpptopdf" target="_blank" rel="noindex,nofollow" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/11/di-ragion-la-trasse-amore-lucia-di-lammermoor-a-novara/?format=pdf" title="Download PDF"><img alt="Download PDF" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/plugins/wp-post-to-pdf/asset/images/pdf.png"></a></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="entry-extra clearfix"><div class="comments-link " style="color: #363636"> <i class="icon-comment"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/11/di-ragion-la-trasse-amore-lucia-di-lammermoor-a-novara/#comments">1 Reply</a></div><div class="entry-share"> <span style="color: #363636">Share This<i class="icon-plus"></i></span><div class="entry-share-icons"> <span class="ct-pinterest" title="Share on Pinterest"><a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http://www.gbopera.it/2012/11/di-ragion-la-trasse-amore-lucia-di-lammermoor-a-novara/&amp;media=http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/LUCIA-DI-LAMMERMOORE-02-1024x610.jpg&amp;description=«Di%20ragion%20la%20trasse%20amore%20…».%20&#8220;Lucia%20di%20Lammermoor&#8221;%20a%20Novara" target="_blank"><i class="icon-pinterest"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-fb" title="Share on Facebook"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http://www.gbopera.it/2012/11/di-ragion-la-trasse-amore-lucia-di-lammermoor-a-novara/" target="_blank"><i class="icon-facebook"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-twitter" title="Share on Twitter"><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=«Di%20ragion%20la%20trasse%20amore%20…».%20&#8220;Lucia%20di%20Lammermoor&#8221;%20a%20Novara&amp;url=http://www.gbopera.it/2012/11/di-ragion-la-trasse-amore-lucia-di-lammermoor-a-novara/" target="_blank"><i class="icon-twitter"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-gplus" title="Share on Google Plus"><a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=http://www.gbopera.it/2012/11/di-ragion-la-trasse-amore-lucia-di-lammermoor-a-novara/